snippet.title: Drill Man Rumble Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Drill Man Rumble will be available on Steam Early Access in Early 2020. Console versions to be announced soon!

Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1072910/Drill_Man_Rumble/
